<paragraph base="F29577337" id="IFRS14_1"><paranum>1</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 14"/><data name="paranum" value="1"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS14_P0005">The objective of this Standard is to specify the financial reporting requirements for <xref base="F29577655" href="IFRS14_APPA.dita#IFRS14_APPA/IFRS14_DI0007" scope="local"><i>regulatory deferral account balances</i><ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0321"/></ph></xref> that arise when an entity provides goods or services to customers at a price or rate that is subject to <xref base="F29577645" href="IFRS14_APPA.dita#IFRS14_APPA/IFRS14_DI0006" scope="local"><i>rate regulation</i><ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0314"/></ph></xref>.</p></body></paragraph>